{
  "texts": [
    "We refer to this code as the[[4, 2, 2]] code to distinguish it from the[[4, 1, 2]] code shown to the right of the figure.The[[4, 2, 2]] code has stabilizer generators S X = X 1 X 2 X 3 X 4 and S Z = Z 1 Z 2 Z 3 Z 4 and logical operators X X X = for logical operators indexed A and B.",
    "The [[4, 1, 2]] code is an error detecting code that encodes a single logical qubit.",
    "It is closely related to the error detecting code shown (left).",
    "It has stabilizer generators S X = X 1 X 2 X 3 X 4, Injecting an encoded magic state into the surface code.",
    "The magic state is initially encoded on a [[4, 1, 2]] code."
  ]
}